<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Talib al-ʿIlm — Islamic Studies Roadmap</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/7.8.5/d3.min.js"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Naskh+Arabic:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══ BASE / SEPIA THEME ══════════════════════════════ */
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#0c0904;--bg2:#130f08;--bg3:#1c1510;
  --gold:#c9a84c;--gold2:#e8c97a;
  --muted:#6b5a3e;--border:#2c1e10;--text:#e8d5b7;
  --pw:292px;
  --mh:#4caf50; /* hanbali */
  --ms:#42a5f5; /* shafi */
  --mm:#ce93d8; /* maliki */
  --mf:#ff8a65; /* hanafi */
}
body{background:var(--bg);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;overflow:hidden;width:100vw;height:100vh;color:var(--text)}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 45% at 12% 20%,rgba(201,168,76,.05) 0%,transparent 65%),
  radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 88% 80%,rgba(160,100,30,.04) 0%,transparent 60%)}

/* ═══ SPLASH ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
#splash{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:9999;background:var(--bg);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:18px;
  cursor:pointer;animation:splashOut .6s ease 2.8s forwards}
@keyframes splashOut{to{opacity:0;pointer-events:none}}
.sp-bism{font-family:'Noto Naskh Arabic',serif;font-size:clamp(52px,9vw,96px);
  color:var(--gold2);line-height:1;text-align:center;
  text-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(232,201,122,.4),0 0 120px rgba(201,168,76,.2);
  opacity:0;animation:spIn 1s ease .3s forwards}
.sp-line{width:90px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);
  opacity:0;animation:spIn .5s ease 1s forwards}
.sp-en{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--muted);opacity:0;animation:spIn .5s ease 1.2s forwards}
@keyframes spIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

/* ═══ TRACK SELECTION SCREEN ════════════════════════ */
#track-screen{
  position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:8000;
  background:rgba(12,9,4,.98);
  display:none;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;
  overflow-y:auto;padding:40px 20px 60px;
  backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
}
#track-screen.show{display:flex}
#track-screen::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}
#track-screen::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)}

.track-inner{width:100%;max-width:680px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:28px}
.track-bism{font-family:'Noto Naskh Arabic',serif;font-size:42px;color:var(--gold2);
  text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(232,201,122,.3);margin-bottom:4px}
.track-title{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:22px;color:var(--gold2);
  letter-spacing:.1em;text-align:center;line-height:1.3}
.track-subtitle{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--muted);text-align:center}
.track-divider{width:180px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,var(--gold),transparent)}

.track-note{
  width:100%;padding:18px 22px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.04);
}
.track-note strong{
  display:block;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:11px;
  letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold2);margin-bottom:8px}
.track-note p{font-size:12px;color:#c8b48a;line-height:1.8}

.track-choose-title{
  font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:14px;
  letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);
  text-align:center}
.track-choose-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;
  letter-spacing:.06em;margin-top:-18px}

.madhab-grid{width:100%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.madhab-grid .m-all{grid-column:1/-1}

.mbtn{
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;
  padding:16px 18px;border:1px solid var(--border);
  background:transparent;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;
  transition:all .2s ease;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.mbtn::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.mbtn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
.mbtn:hover::before{opacity:1}
.mbtn .m-name{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase}
.mbtn .m-desc{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.4}
.mbtn .m-imam{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--muted);font-style:italic}

.mbtn.han{border-color:#4caf5033}
.mbtn.han::before{background:rgba(76,175,80,.06)}
.mbtn.han .m-name{color:#81c784}
.mbtn.han:hover{border-color:#4caf5066}

.mbtn.sha{border-color:#42a5f533}
.mbtn.sha::before{background:rgba(66,165,245,.06)}
.mbtn.sha .m-name{color:#64b5f6}
.mbtn.sha:hover{border-color:#42a5f566}

.mbtn.mal{border-color:#ce93d833}
.mbtn.mal::before{background:rgba(206,147,216,.06)}
.mbtn.mal .m-name{color:#ce93d8}
.mbtn.mal:hover{border-color:#ce93d866}

.mbtn.haf{border-color:#ff8a6533}
.mbtn.haf::before{background:rgba(255,138,101,.06)}
.mbtn.haf .m-name{color:#ff8a65}
.mbtn.haf:hover{border-color:#ff8a6566}

.mbtn.all{border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.3)}
.mbtn.all::before{background:rgba(201,168,76,.05)}
.mbtn.all .m-name{color:var(--gold2)}
.mbtn.all:hover{border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.6)}

.track-change-note{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--muted);text-align:center}

/* ═══ HEADER ════════════════════════════════════════ */
#header{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:46px;z-index:200;
  background:rgba(12,9,4,.97);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow:0 1px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.55);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 12px;gap:8px;will-change:transform}
#header h1{font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;
  color:var(--gold);white-space:nowrap;text-transform:uppercase;
  text-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(201,168,76,.28)}
.hsep{width:1px;height:18px;background:var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.legend{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;overflow:hidden;flex-wrap:nowrap}
.chip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;font-size:7px;letter-spacing:.03em;
  color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:2px;
  border:1px solid transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:all .16s;user-select:none}
.chip:hover{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:var(--text)}
.chip.active{color:#0c0904}
.chip .ld{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.hbtn{margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:4px;flex-shrink:0}
.hbtn button{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.07em;
  padding:4px 8px;cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;transition:all .16s;white-space:nowrap}
.hbtn button:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,168,76,.07)}
.hbtn button.active{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,168,76,.1)}
#btn-search{font-size:13px;padding:3px 8px}
#madhab-badge{
  padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;
  letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  border:1px solid;cursor:pointer;transition:all .16s;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;white-space:nowrap;
}
#madhab-badge:hover{filter:brightness(1.2)}

/* ═══ SEARCH ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
#search-wrap{position:fixed;top:56px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  z-index:500;width:420px;max-width:92vw;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .18s}
#search-wrap.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
#search-input{width:100%;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(19,15,8,.99);
  border:1px solid var(--gold);color:var(--text);
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;outline:none;
  box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.65)}
#search-input::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}
#search-results{background:rgba(19,15,8,.99);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-top:none;max-height:290px;overflow-y:auto}
#search-results::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}
#search-results::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)}
.sr-item{padding:9px 14px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .12s}
.sr-item:hover{background:rgba(201,168,76,.07)}
.sr-name{font-size:10px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.35}
.sr-name.mem{color:var(--gold2)}
.sr-path{font-size:8px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;letter-spacing:.05em}
.sr-none{padding:12px 14px;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center}

/* ═══ BREADCRUMB ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#breadcrumb{position:fixed;top:58px;left:16px;z-index:150;pointer-events:none;
  font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;
  opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s;max-width:55vw;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
#breadcrumb.show{opacity:1}
#breadcrumb span{color:var(--gold2)}

/* ═══ CANVAS ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
#canvas{width:100%;height:100%;cursor:grab;display:block;will-change:transform;transform:translateZ(0)}
#canvas:active{cursor:grabbing}

/* ═══ PANEL ════════════════════════════════════════════ */
#panel{position:fixed;right:0;top:46px;bottom:0;width:var(--pw);
  background:rgba(19,15,8,.98);border-left:1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow:-6px 0 28px rgba(0,0,0,.5);z-index:300;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  transform:translateX(var(--pw));
  transition:transform .28s cubic-bezier(.34,1.15,.64,1);
  will-change:transform;overflow-y:auto;backdrop-filter:blur(16px)}
#panel.open{transform:translateX(0)}
#panel::-webkit-scrollbar{width:2px}
#panel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)}
#panel-close{position:sticky;top:0;align-self:flex-end;margin:10px 10px -4px auto;
  background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;
  transition:color .16s;z-index:1;line-height:1}
#panel-close:hover{color:var(--gold)}
#panel-path{padding:12px 14px 0;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.9}
#panel-path span{color:var(--gold2)}
#panel-title{padding:10px 14px 12px;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:12px;
  color:var(--gold2);line-height:1.45;border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-left:none;border-right:none;margin-top:8px;
  text-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(232,201,122,.18)}
#panel-mem{padding:10px 14px 2px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.12em;
  color:var(--gold2);min-height:28px;text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(232,201,122,.4)}
#panel-btns{padding:12px 14px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.pbtn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 13px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--text);
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.06em;
  cursor:pointer;text-align:left;transition:all .18s;text-decoration:none;width:100%}
.pbtn:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold2);background:rgba(201,168,76,.06);
  box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(201,168,76,.1);transform:translateX(2px)}
.pbtn .icon{font-size:13px;width:18px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;opacity:.8}
#panel-note{padding:12px 14px 18px;font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.7;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:auto}

/* ═══ CONTROLS ════════════════════════════════════════ */
#controls{position:fixed;bottom:14px;right:14px;display:flex;gap:4px;z-index:150}
.cbtn{width:28px;height:28px;background:rgba(19,15,8,.9);border:1px solid var(--border);
  color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;transition:all .16s;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
.cbtn:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)}
#hint{position:fixed;bottom:14px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#251a0a;pointer-events:none;
  text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;transition:opacity .3s}

/* ═══ LIST VIEW ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
#listview{position:fixed;top:46px;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;overflow-y:auto;background:var(--bg);display:none;z-index:50}
#listview.show{display:block}
#listview::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}
#listview::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border)}
.lv-level{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.lv-lhdr{padding:13px 14px;font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;user-select:none;transition:background .16s}
.lv-lhdr:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.018)}
.lv-lhdr .ct,.lv-shdr .ct{font-size:10px;transition:transform .24s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);color:var(--muted);flex-shrink:0}
.lv-lhdr.open .ct,.lv-shdr.open .ct{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.lv-lbody{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .34s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}
.lv-lbody.open{max-height:20000px}
.lv-subject{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
.lv-shdr{padding:8px 22px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;user-select:none;transition:background .13s}
.lv-shdr:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.015)}
.lv-shdr.grayed{opacity:.2}
.lv-shdr .ct{margin-left:auto}
.lv-sbody{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .26s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);padding:0 28px}
.lv-sbody.open{max-height:5000px;padding-bottom:10px}
.lv-book{display:flex;align-items:center;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.02);gap:6px;min-height:29px}
.lv-book-num{font-size:8px;color:var(--muted);width:14px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:right}
.lv-book-name{font-size:9.5px;opacity:.72;flex:1;line-height:1.35;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .13s}
.lv-book-name:hover{opacity:1}
.lv-book-name.is-mem{color:var(--gold2);opacity:1;
  text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(232,201,122,.45),0 0 18px rgba(201,168,76,.22);
  animation:mpulse 3.2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes mpulse{0%,100%{text-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(232,201,122,.4),0 0 14px rgba(201,168,76,.18)}
  50%{text-shadow:0 0 11px rgba(232,201,122,.7),0 0 26px rgba(201,168,76,.38)}}
.lv-book-actions{display:flex;gap:3px;flex-shrink:0}
.lv-btn{width:20px;height:20px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);
  color:var(--muted);font-size:9px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;text-decoration:none;transition:all .14s;line-height:1}
.lv-btn:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,168,76,.08)}

/* ═══ MOBILE ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
@media(max-width:700px){
  #header{padding:0 8px;gap:6px;height:50px}
  #header h1{font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.12em}
  .legend{display:none}.hsep{display:none}
  .hbtn{gap:3px}.hbtn button{font-size:8px;padding:4px 6px}
  #btn-search{font-size:12px;padding:4px 7px}
  #canvas{touch-action:none}
  #panel{width:100vw;top:50px;border-left:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    transform:translateY(100%);transition:transform .28s cubic-bezier(.34,1.15,.64,1)}
  #panel.open{transform:translateY(0)}
  #panel-title{font-size:13px;padding:12px 16px}
  #panel-path{padding:14px 16px 0;font-size:10px}
  #panel-mem{padding:10px 16px 0;font-size:10px}
  #panel-btns{padding:14px 16px 18px;gap:9px}
  .pbtn{padding:13px 16px;font-size:11px}.pbtn .icon{font-size:15px}
  #panel-close{font-size:18px;margin:12px 12px -4px auto}
  #search-wrap{width:96vw;top:60px}
  #search-input{font-size:12px;padding:12px 14px}
  .sr-item{padding:11px 14px}.sr-name{font-size:11px}.sr-path{font-size:9px}
  #breadcrumb{top:60px;font-size:8.5px;max-width:80vw}
  #listview{top:50px}
  .lv-lhdr{padding:14px 14px;font-size:11px}
  .lv-shdr{padding:10px 20px;font-size:9.5px}
  .lv-sbody{padding:0 20px}.lv-sbody.open{padding-bottom:12px}
  .lv-book{min-height:38px;padding:6px 0;gap:8px}
  .lv-book-name{font-size:10px}
  .lv-btn{width:26px;height:26px;font-size:11px}
  #controls{bottom:20px;right:12px}.cbtn{width:34px;height:34px;font-size:16px}
  #hint{display:none}
  .madhab-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .track-title{font-size:18px}.track-bism{font-size:36px}
}
@supports(padding:max(0px)){
  #header{padding-left:max(12px,env(safe-area-inset-left));padding-right:max(12px,env(safe-area-inset-right))}
  #listview{padding-bottom:env(safe-area-inset-bottom)}
  #panel{padding-bottom:env(safe-area-inset-bottom)}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- SPLASH -->
<div id="splash" onclick="dismissSplash()">
  <div class="sp-bism">&#xFDFD;</div>
  <div class="sp-line"></div>
  <div class="sp-en">In the name of Allah, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful</div>
</div>

<!-- TRACK SELECTION SCREEN -->
<div id="track-screen">
  <div class="track-inner">
    <div class="track-bism">&#xFDFD;</div>
    <h2 class="track-title">Welcome, Talib al-ʿIlm</h2>
    <p class="track-subtitle">Your Path to Islamic Scholarship</p>
    <div class="track-divider"></div>

    <div class="track-note">
      <strong>❀ On Intention — al-Niyyah</strong>
      <p>
        The Messenger of Allah ﷺ said:<br>
        <em>"Actions are only by intentions, and every person will have only what they intended. Whoever emigrates for the sake of Allah and His Messenger, his emigration is for Allah and His Messenger. And whoever emigrates to gain something of this world or to marry a woman, his emigration is for whatever he emigrated for."</em><br>
        — Sahih al-Bukhari 1 · Sahih Muslim 1907
        <br><br>
        He ﷺ also said: <em>"Whoever Allah wishes good for, He grants him understanding (fiqh) of the religion."</em><br>
        — Sahih al-Bukhari 71 · Sahih Muslim 1037
        <br><br>
        Before opening any book, check your heart. You are not studying to debate, to gain status, or to be called a scholar. You are studying to act upon what you learn and to draw closer to Allah. The one who learns without acting is warned in the Quran itself (Surah al-Saff 61:2–3).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="track-note">
      <strong>📖 Study with a Qualified Shaykh</strong>
      <p>
        This roadmap is a guide only — it does not replace a living teacher.
        The scholars unanimously warn: <em>"Whoever takes his knowledge from books alone has more errors than correct answers."</em>
        Seek a Shaykh with a connected chain of transmission (isnād), sound creed (ʿaqīdah), and upright character.
        Even reading a sharḥ (explanation) is not a substitute — the teacher corrects your pronunciation, your understanding, and your methodology.
        If you cannot find a local Shaykh, study online with qualified teachers from established institutions such as IUM Madinah, IMSIU Riyadh, or Umm al-Qura Makkah.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="track-choose-title">Choose Your Fiqh Specialization</p>
    <p class="track-choose-sub">All four madhabs follow the Salafi ʿaqīdah. Choose your fiqh track. All other sciences remain fully visible for everyone.</p>

    <div class="madhab-grid">
      <button class="mbtn han" onclick="chooseTrack('hanbali')">
        <span class="m-name">Hanbali</span>
        <span class="m-imam">Imam Ahmad ibn Hanbal (d. 241 AH)</span>
        <span class="m-desc">Dominant in Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Gulf region. The official school of the Saudi state. Strong emphasis on texts (Quran &amp; Sunnah) over analogy.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="mbtn sha" onclick="chooseTrack('shafi')">
        <span class="m-name">Shafi&#x02BF;i</span>
        <span class="m-imam">Imam Muhammad ibn Idris al-Shafi&#x02BF;i (d. 204 AH)</span>
        <span class="m-desc">Dominant in Egypt, Levant, East Africa, SE Asia, Yemen. Known for the most systematic usool al-fiqh methodology.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="mbtn mal" onclick="chooseTrack('maliki')">
        <span class="m-name">Maliki</span>
        <span class="m-imam">Imam Malik ibn Anas (d. 179 AH)</span>
